# ⚔️ Ironhold Chess

> **Two armies. One board. No mercy.**

**Ironhold Chess** is a cinematic browser-based chess experience where traditional chess meets animated battlefield combat.

Instead of static chess pieces, every piece is represented as a unique warrior silhouette with custom SVG artwork, animated combat sequences, sound effects, visual themes, and an AI opponent.

🌐 **Live Demo:** `https://adithyanhp.github.io/Ironhold-Chess/`

---

## 🎮 Features

### ♟️ Complete Chess Gameplay

* Standard chess board and movement rules
* Legal move validation
* Check detection
* Checkmate detection
* Stalemate and draw detection
* Castling
* En passant
* Pawn promotion
* Move history
* Captured piece tracking
* Material advantage calculation
* Board flipping

### ⚔️ Animated Battle System

Every capture becomes a battlefield encounter.

* Piece-specific attack animations
* Animated attacker movement
* Defender impact reactions
* Knockback and collapse effects
* Impact flashes
* Smoke effects
* Board shake effects
* Unique animation styles for different piece types

The goal is to make every capture feel like an actual clash between two armies.

### 🛡️ Unique Warrior Pieces

Each chess piece has its own visual identity:

| Chess Piece | Warrior Design           |
| ----------- | ------------------------ |
| ♙ Pawn      | Foot Soldier             |
| ♘ Knight    | Mounted Warrior          |
| ♗ Bishop    | Hooded Mystic            |
| ♖ Rook      | Hulking Guardian         |
| ♕ Queen     | Regal Twin-Blade Warrior |
| ♔ King      | Crowned Warlord          |

All character artwork is created using custom SVG shapes and CSS animations.

### 🤖 Ironhold AI

Play against the built-in AI opponent.

Available difficulty levels:

* **Recruit** — Easy
* **Veteran** — Medium
* **Warlord** — Hard

The AI uses a chess evaluation system that considers:

* Material value
* Piece positioning
* Mobility
* King safety
* Tactical opportunities

### 🎨 Multiple Army Themes

Customize the battlefield with different visual palettes:

* 🟡 Molten Gold vs Deep Obsidian
* 🔵 Neon vs Shadow
* ❄️ Ice vs Fire
* 🩸 Bone vs Blood Moon

### 🔊 Sound Effects

The game includes procedural sound effects using the Web Audio API.

* Piece movement sounds
* Capture sounds
* Check notifications
* Combat impact effects

Sound can be enabled or disabled at any time.

### 📜 Battle Chronicle

Track the entire game through the move history panel.

The game displays:

* Move numbers
* White moves
* Black moves
* Captured pieces
* Material advantage

### 📱 Responsive Design

Ironhold Chess is designed to work across different screen sizes.

* Desktop
* Laptop
* Tablet
* Mobile devices

The board automatically adapts to the available screen width.

