## 🕹️ How to Play

### Play Online

Open the live demo:

```text
https://adithyanhp.github.io/Ironhold-Chess/
```

### Run Locally

Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/adithyanhp/ironhold-chess.git
```

Open the project directory:

```bash
cd ironhold-chess
```

Then open:

```text
index.html
```

in any modern web browser.

No installation or build process is required.

---

## 🧩 Controls

| Action           | Control                   |
| ---------------- | ------------------------- |
| Select a piece   | Click                     |
| Move a piece     | Click a legal destination |
| Promote a pawn   | Select a promotion piece  |
| Undo a move      | Undo Move button          |
| Rotate the board | Flip Board button         |
| Change theme     | Army Colors               |
| Toggle sound     | Sound button              |
| Start a new game | New Campaign              |

