## 🎯 Project Vision

Most browser chess games focus purely on the board.

**Ironhold Chess focuses on the battle.**

The goal is to create a chess experience where every move feels meaningful and every capture feels like a clash between two opposing forces.

> **Chess is strategy.**
>
> **Ironhold Chess is strategy at war.**

